              <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq('faq1')">If my car is stolen, does it really alert me?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></button>
              <div class="faq-a">Yes. Tracki features an internal accelerometer. You can set it to push a notification or send an SMS text message to your phone the exact second the car is moved, giving you a massive head start before they get too far.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item" id="faq2">
              <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq('faq2')">Will it drain my car's battery?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></button>
              <div class="faq-a">No. The Tracki Pro runs entirely on its own internal 10,000mAh rechargeable battery. It draws zero power from your vehicle's electrical system. Nothing is plugged into your car at all — completely wired-free.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item" id="faq3">
              <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq('faq3')">Can a thief detect it with a signal scanner?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></button>
              <div class="faq-a">Unlike Bluetooth tags that actively announce themselves, the Tracki Pro transmits standard 4G cellular data — the same signal as any smartphone. A thief would need dedicated equipment and to know exactly what they're looking for.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item" id="faq4">
              <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq('faq4')">How do I share live tracking with police?<span class="faq-icon">+</span></button>
